@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "Privacy Policy";
}

<h1>@ViewData["Title"]</h1>

<p>
    At <strong>cShipment</strong>, we are committed to protecting the privacy and confidentiality of all individuals who interact with our transport logistics platform. This Privacy Policy outlines how we collect, use, disclose, and safeguard your information.
</p>

<h2>1. Information We Collect</h2>
<ul>
    <li><strong>Customer Data:</strong> Name, contact details, shipment history, delivery locations, and payment records.</li>
    <li><strong>Driver Data:</strong> Name, license number, assigned shipments, driving history.</li>
    <li><strong>Truck Data:</strong> Vehicle ID, assigned drivers and shipments.</li>
    <li><strong>Usage Data:</strong> IP address, login sessions, route activity, device/browser type.</li>
</ul>

<h2>2. How We Use the Information</h2>
<ul>
    <li>To assign and manage shipments, trucks, and drivers.</li>
    <li>To optimize delivery routes and reduce operational costs.</li>
    <li>To maintain accurate truck maintenance logs.</li>
    <li>To generate reports for business analysis and regulatory compliance.</li>
    <li>To send operational notifications and updates to users.</li>
</ul>

<h2>3. Sharing and Disclosure</h2>
<ul>
    <li>We do not sell or rent personal data to third parties.</li>
    <li>Information may be shared with logistics partners, authorities, or maintenance vendors when necessary for operations or legal obligations.</li>
    <li>All third-party access is governed by strict confidentiality agreements and access control policies.</li>
</ul>

<h2>4. Data Security</h2>
<ul>
    <li>All user data is stored in a secure database with encryption-at-rest and in-transit.</li>
    <li>Role-based access control (RBAC) is enforced to restrict data access.</li>
    <li>We conduct regular security audits and comply with industry best practices for data protection.</li>
</ul>

<h2>5. Your Rights and Choices</h2>
<ul>
    <li>You may request access to your personal data.</li>
    <li>You may correct or update your information from within the platform or by contacting support.</li>
    <li>You may request deletion of your account and data (unless required to retain by law).</li>
</ul>

<h2>6. Data Retention</h2>
<p>
    We retain data only as long as necessary to fulfill shipment records, taxation, safety compliance, and other legal requirements. Once no longer needed, it is securely deleted.
</p>

<h2>7. Children's Privacy</h2>
<p>
    cShipment does not knowingly collect information from individuals under the age of 18.
</p>

<h2>8. Policy Updates</h2>
<p>
    We may update this Privacy Policy as our system evolves. Changes will be communicated via our platform or email, and the updated policy will be posted here.
</p>

<h2>9. Contact Us</h2>
<p>
    For questions or concerns about this policy or your data, contact us at <a href="mailto:support@cshipment.com">support@cshipment.com</a>.
</p>
